metadata.title: Ownership Boundaries - CNF

creators.name: USDA Forest Service, Chugach National Forest

metadata.description: Data Type: Boundaries; Cover type layer with area of polygon in square meters, perimeter of polygon in ownership code including conveyances and selected lands. Conveyed lands depicted are primarily conveyances to the State and Native Corporations. Smaller parcels are being added as time and information become available. Scale is 1:63,360/40 acres.
